long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Chrome extension, developed by Octavebytes, enables the communication between HubSpot and the Octavebytes AWS CTI Connector. It allows users to manage both inbound & outbound calls directly from within the HubSpot interface, providing a more efficient and integrated workflow.
